{/* Hero Section */}

Silver Era Transition

The European Crossroad for Generational Transitions

{/* Comparison Section */}

The old way

The SET way

Sole Focus on Financials

Traditional methods overlook interpersonal and cultural factors that are critical for a successful transition.

Time-Consuming and Inefficient

Brokers and sellers rely on personal networks, making the process slow and prone to mismatches.

High Failure Rates

Mismatches in expectations or poor cultural alignment frequently lead to failed negotiations or post-sale challenges.

Cultural and Interpersonal Alignment

SET prioritizes cultural fit and interpersonal compatibility, ensuring smoother transitions and long-term success for businesses.

Preserving Legacy

SET helps sellers find successors who align with their values and vision, ensuring their life's work continues authentically.

Streamlined Process

SET’s structured platform saves time by filtering and matching based on key personal and business factors.

{/* Process Section */}

Jumpstarting the journey

Data Collection/Integration

We collect and streamline all necessary data, wishes, and wants.

Matchmaking

We immediately are able to provide the best matches from our database.

Initial Contact

Once matched, partner brokers and advisors continue the process.

{/* USP Section */}

Why interpersonal aspects?

SET eliminates the number 1 cause for M&A failures occurring 70 to 90%.

  • Precision

    Free-text response analysis, matchmaking users based not only on keywords but on the underlying meanings and contexts.

  • Customization

    Filter-based system. Select your hard requirements and tell us their priority.

  • Opportunity Maximization

    Discover opportunities you might have missed with only 1 broker. Work with a combined network of brokers and advisors.
